==English==
===Noun===
'''housemaid'''
#A female servant attached to the non-servant quarter part of the house. (as opposed to a scullery maid.)
#(derogatory) a housewife.
===Verb===
#To be a housemaid.
#To wait on someone hand on foot, to watch them.

